item.title: Speaking at SharePoint Fest Seattle 2018
item.author: vbiret+blog@outlook.com (Vincent Biret)
item.description: SharePoint Fest Seattle 2018 is happening from August 20th to 24th. This event will feature 2 days pre-conference workshops and 3 days of conference. You can find more information about it on the website. I’ve been selected amongst 74 other speakers (including people from Microsoft product teams!!) to present this year two sessions: AZR203 - Azure Functions In The Real World: Lessons Learned & Best Practices “Azure Functions is one of the most powerful new solutions provided by Microsoft.
